data.description: Nestled in a quiet neighborhood, well kept 2 story home offers an enticing blend of timeless charm. With 4 spacious bedrooms and 3.1 bathrooms. The exterior of the home exudes Mediterranean allure with its red-tiled roof, and lush landscaping. A charming water feature in the front sets a tranquil tone from the moment you arrive. An electric gate ensures privacy and security, while turn-on switches for holiday lighting make seasonal decorating a breeze. The kitchen boasts all-new appliances, the refrigerator conveys. The living area opens to a large deck, perfect for outdoor dining and relaxation. The first floor includes 2 large bedrooms with an en-suite bathroom, while the remaining bedrooms and bathrooms offer ample space. Outside, has 2 sheds, and an oversized carport. This home truly offers modern conveniences, and outdoor spaces that invite you to savor the pleasant weather. A rare find in a highly desirable neighborhood, it's an opportunity not to be missed.
